    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class manages digested Messages. Each entry is boiled down to the function, and an array of targets. The targets are actually stored on the <ref refid="classMsg" kindref="compound">Msg</ref>, but they referenced in the <ref refid="classMsgDigest" kindref="compound">MsgDigest</ref>. As a further refinement, if the target DataIndex is ALLDATA, then it means that all data entries in the target are to be iterated over. Note that this does not extend to <ref refid="classField" kindref="compound">Field</ref> targets. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
